네, 요청하신 대로 Technical Field와 Summary of the Invention의 후반부(Technical Advantages 포함) 원문을 번역 없이 그대로 옮겨드리고, 이를 바탕으로 한 다이어그램을 정리해 드립니다.
📄 US9867039: Technical Field & Summary (Original Text)
Technical Field
> The present invention relates generally to wireless communications, and more particularly to a system and method for faked base station detection.
> 
Summary of the Invention (Advantages & Mechanism)
> Technical advantages are generally achieved, by embodiments of this disclosure which describe a system and method for faked base station detection.
> In accordance with an embodiment, a method for faked base station (BS) detection is provided. The method includes: obtaining, by a first wireless device, a plurality of parameters associated with a discovery signal transmitted by a second wireless device advertising as a BS; comparing, by the first wireless device, the plurality of parameters with a set of parameters assigned to or associated with a cluster of neighboring BSs; and determining that the second wireless device is a faked BS when a discrepancy between the plurality of parameters and the set of parameters associated with the cluster of neighboring BSs exceeds a threshold.
> In accordance with another embodiment, a first wireless device is provided. The first wireless device includes: a processor; and a computer readable storage medium storing programming for execution by the processor, the programming including instructions to: identify a plurality of parameters associated with a discovery signal transmitted by a second wireless device advertising as a base station (BS); and transmit the plurality of parameters to a central controller.
> 
📊 Mechanism & Advantages (Mermaid Diagram)
원문의 **"비교 및 판단 로직"**과 "중앙 컨트롤러 전송" 이라는 두 가지 핵심 실시예를 통합한 다이어그램입니다.
graph TD
    %% 노드 정의
    FBS["Second Wireless Device <br/> (Advertising as BS)"]
    WD1["First Wireless Device <br/> (UE or BS)"]
    CC["Central Controller"]
    
    %% 프로세스 흐름
    FBS -- "Transmits Discovery Signal" --> WD1
    
    subgraph "Internal Processing (WD1)"
        A["Identify Plurality of Parameters"]
        B{"Compare with <br/> Cluster Parameters"}
        C["DETERMINE FAKED BS"]
    end

    WD1 --> A
    A --> B
    B -- "Discrepancy > Threshold" --> C
    
    %% 중앙 컨트롤러 전송 실시예
    A -. "Transmit Parameters" .-> CC
    CC -. "Aggregate, Correlate, Analyze" .-> CC

    %% 스타일 설정 (텍스트 잘림 방지 및 색상)
